projects.description:
This project aims to develop a comprehensive Postman workspace for Google's Gemini API, providing a central hub for exploration, integration, and troubleshooting. The plan is to create a well-organized API collection covering all Gemini functionalities (text generation, image/video/audio analysis, and code generation), with configured environments for development and production. 

Deliverables include:
1. Pre-built Postman API collection;
2. Detailed technical documentation within Postman;
3. Mock server for offline development/testing;
4. Automated update mechanism via GitHub Actions. 

This project will significantly reduce the learning curve for developers adopting Gemini API, promote best practices, and establish a sustainable framework that evolves alongside Google's Generative AI offerings.
